Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正无聊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在刚才有一封很奇怪的信寄给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 读出来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「试一试预测自己的未来」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FROM制作组人员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.16,0:00:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你能预测到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然只能是个半吊子的秀才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你能预测吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要指引出未来的 先追寻历史就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回忆从我们相遇开始至今所经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.69,0:00:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长话短说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:01:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(426,338)}春天到来的GOSICK特番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:01:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(425,372)}美丽的怪物严重的混沌未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冷 漆黑 阴郁的高塔里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个纤细的女孩被关在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤单的女孩 仅仅追求的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装得满满的甜点心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多的书籍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H000008&\fs24\pos(425,372)\fad(400,300)}随春而来的死神讲述逝去的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1924年 春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口说人话 头脑清晰的灰色之狼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说话的狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个倒也许能友好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天我追寻着金色之光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就像被什么引导着那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊 随春而来的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你被选中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为填补我无聊的混沌碎片之一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我和维多利加的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之后 我们不断被卷入不可思议的事件和谜团当中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人事件不断发生 并伴随着不可思议的谜团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 维多利加通过自己的「智慧之泉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世上的混沌再现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.11,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很小巧 但却也是令人觉得不可思议的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 维多利加不仅仅是脑袋聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}+还很会卖萌~~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又陷入无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了解我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想了解的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有一点点傲慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑起来也怪怪地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来这种笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时又滚来滚去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生起气来 就马上鼓起脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你说教 让我十分不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说必需就是必需
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是给她甜点心的话 心情就会变好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷公米花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直硬的不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 你觉得很好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样没错 因为是零食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明长一副狗屎样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次拿什么给她好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不是维多利加的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我从久城身边滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个男人 是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事都能用「智慧之泉」解决的维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也有不擅长的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以说是 很有自己的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以洗泡澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么情况 就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢泡澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 我还以为是呼叫声 就有些着急了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.28,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说不擅长 但又很有维多利加的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她喜欢作弄人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候我也受了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 听说你因为穿它感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个小笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 说我是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偷偷藏着这张纸 要帮我保密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊死了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.76,0:06:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还藏着很多我不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持有维多利加过去的钥匙之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的异母兄弟古雷温·德·布洛瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然被人们称为名警官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实只是依靠维多利加破案
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把功劳归到自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官不知为何不和维多利加对上眼睛说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官和维多利加之间有着我不知道的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有爱过任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 你小小的身体上 究竟负担着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本世纪最伟大魔术师布莱恩·罗斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这名字好像在哪里听过…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是罗斯可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是瞬间移动的罗斯可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个的魔术师 除了有一头火红的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有着和维多利加一样的绿色的瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么形容 他总是带着莫明的忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚·盖洛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯蒂丽亚·盖洛 是我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.19,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲曾经是一名舞女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豪华的装扮 异国风情的装容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有灰狼村子的出身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.94,0:08:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布洛瓦侯爵试图把灰狼的特殊能力移植到自己的族人中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把柯蒂丽亚占为己有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后不久 我就诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 布洛瓦侯爵还是知道了母亲的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲是个罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加相信母亲的无辜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并决定作为女儿的自己要证明她清白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯蒂丽亚的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直一模一样 快看那张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长老
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是受我的信息召唤而来的子孙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有驱逐的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们一起来庆祝夏至祭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便这个女孩的母亲柯蒂丽亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是罪人——C
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是柯蒂丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 杀死了我的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狄奥多大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荷曼妮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认 杀了你的人正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.37,0:09:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和你推理的一样 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧久城 别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得和你相处融洽起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可受不了再次绝交
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种情况下说什么无所谓的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是无所谓的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的罪孽这样就洗清了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.59,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后 维多利加拿出了无罪的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 神谕却说出了那种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个都不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离现在几年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吹起撼动世界的狂风
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的身体太过轻盈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被狂风吹散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.90,0:11:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么慌张的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的项链会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的东西要好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼睛啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也说过了吧 要一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝不会在这里分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.97,0:12:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里分开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心是永远分不开的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到一直以来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定能克服困难的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧 维多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你对我是怎么想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同班同学？下仆？笨蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 只有这件事请不要忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.82,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利加 无论发生什么我都会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不是孤单一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了很多事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.72,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是感慨的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己试试把混沌碎片再构成出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给点提示
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就调查一下和你有关系的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个跟你很像的家伙过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H1D232C&\3c&HDBDBE9&}GOSICK声优 special talk
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被维多利加差遣来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城一弥的声优 江口拓也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部作品的CAST似乎已经聚齐在里边了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这就去聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.51,0:13:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录节目中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉 我现在 稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之各位 拜托做自我介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是维多利加的声优 悠木碧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞西尔的声优 鹿野优以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾薇儿的声优 下屋则子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天请各位多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.76,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 为了给各位献上美好的访谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备了这样的企划 题目是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gosick 关键词讲故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色死神问出妖精们的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有一个装满卡片的盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里边有写着关键词的混沌碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依次抽出两张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这两个关键词再构成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照给定主题讲一个包含关键词的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么个企划
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话时间是每人30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30秒其实很短哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(300,0)}首先是鹿野优以的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:04.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主题是「配音现场的秘闻」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘闻要在30秒内说出哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这个和这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「才没有XX（傲娇状）」+「半吊子秀才」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用这两个词串故事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要表现配音现场的秘闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(610,92)}话题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(587,175)}配音现场的秘闻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(610,206)}关键词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(561,303)}「~才没有XX（傲娇状）」+「半吊子秀才」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.17,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 碧酱很擅长绘画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在台本上画来画去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.67,0:15:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在画在画
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 我在她旁边经常看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.59,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饰演半吊子秀才的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.32,0:15:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\pos(199,358)\c&H010100&\3c&HEFEFF3&\be3}半吊子秀才 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个谁来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs28}是江口哦 江口撒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然名字想不起来了 但是个男生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.70,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样翘着二郎腿坐着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是让我觉的块头好大的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于艾薇儿役的则子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没有说讨厌或是喜欢什么的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H010100&\3c&HEFEFF3&\be3\pos(249,344)}~才没有XX（傲娇状） 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶上了呢 赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(500,0)}接下来是下屋则子的挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要揭晓主题了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢 什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的下屋则子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我点不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我非常不爽撒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么爽还是不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是Gosick的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对 要优先关键词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「春」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 「春」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和「假装成XX」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(610,92)}话题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(718,141)}最近的下屋则子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(609,204)}关键词
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(603,317)}春和假装成XX
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话我现在正在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要减肥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假装成想做在春天邂逅的幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H010100&\3c&HEFEFF3&\be3\pos(148,353)}春 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8\c&H010100&\3c&HEFEFF3&\be3\pos(183,328)}假装成XX 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.36,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实是向着夏天在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我开始练减压瑜伽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,减压瑜伽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道减压吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆出这样柔软的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在如此减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是最近的下屋则子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\fad(500,0)}最后是悠木碧的挑战！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GOSICK今后的展开是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.52,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击性的事实+说话以喵结句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每句话都要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在就开始喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就行了吗喵?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃有这种兴趣吗喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是碧酱！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.24,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让人头痛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(610,92)}话题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\c&H000105&\3c&HF7FAF8&\pos(573,176)}GOSICK今后的展开是！？
